These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
There 7 different types of food: cauliflower, kale, radish, blueberry, raspberry, cucumber, strawberry
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, biathlon, cycling, parkour, skiing, volleyball
 1. the person eating cauliflower is between the person eating blueberry and the person eating strawberry##2
 2. the person eating kale is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person eating raspberry is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's sport is parkour##2
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
 7. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
 8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
 9. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
10. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
11. the person eating cucumber is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Food   | blueberry | cauliflower | strawberry | kale    | radish | raspberry   | cucumber    |
| Sport         | skiing  | baseball   | cycling | badminton | biathlon   | volleyball | parkour |

