.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  firefighter, dancer, freelancer, chef, security-guard, engineer, paramedic
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, chinese, italian, pakistani, polish, russian, turkish
1. the russian is on the far left##1
2. the freelancer is between the engineer and the russian##2
3. the chinese is on the right of the australian##1
4. the paramedic is on the right of the italian##1
5. the dancer is in the middle##1
6. the polish is on the left of the australian##1
7. the turkish is on the left of the dancer##1
8. the security-guard is on the left of the pakistani##1
9. the chef is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Job          | security-guard | freelancer | engineer | dancer | paramedic | firefighter      | chef  |
| Nationality   | russian | pakistani  | turkish     | italian     | polish  | australian | chinese |

