.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: sunflower, poppy, dahlia, azalea, begonia, lily, daffodil
7 different pets are kept: fish, goat, hamster, pony, rabbit, rat, turtle
 1. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 2. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 3. the owner of the rabbit is the person who growsdaffodil##1
 4. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who growslily##1
 5. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 6. the person who growsazalea is the owner of the pony##1
 7. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 8. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the turtle and the person who growsazalea##2
 9. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
10. the person who growspoppy is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Flower   | daffodil | begonia | sunflower | poppy   | azalea | dahlia | lily |
| Pet           | rabbit | rat     | goat     | hamster | pony   | fish   | turtle    |

