.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, juice, lemonade, sprite, tea, water
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: january, october, may, december, june, august, march
 1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person drinking juice and the person who's birthday is in august##2
 7. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the person who's birthday is in january is the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | juice    | sprite  | lemonade  | fanta  | water      | tea       | iced-tea |
| Birthday   | june | december | august | march | january | may | october  |

