.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: family, mystery, sports, animation, crime, spy, comedy
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, motorbike, ship, skateboard, train, van
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person driving the bike is between the person watching comedy movies and the person watching family movies##2
4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person driving the bike is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the train is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is the person watching animation movies##1
9. the person watching crime movies is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Movie-Genre   | animation      | crime | family | sports | comedy      | mystery      | spy |
| Transport     | helicopter | train | van       | bike | motorbike | skateboard | ship |

