3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the paramedic is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
5. the videographer is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is camping and the firefighter##2
7. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
8. the videographer is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Job     | scientist | firefighter | project-manager | videographer | paramedic | pilot     | writer |
| Hobby   | traveling   | dancing    | fishing    | camping      | sudoku  | card-games | filmmaking |

