.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: chestnut, ivory, emerald, lavender, turquise, brown, blood-red
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, parkour, rowing, rugby, surfing, volleyball
 1. the person who's sport is surfing is the person who likes turquise##1
 2. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 3. the person who's sport is cycling is in the middle##1
 4. the person who likes emerald is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
 6. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who likes chestnut##1
 8. the person who likes brown is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who likes turquise##2
10. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person who likes brown##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Color   | chestnut | ivory    | lavender | emerald   | brown | blood-red    | turquise |
| Sport      | rowing | cricket | volleyball    | cycling | rugby    | parkour | surfing  |

