 8. the accountant is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
 9. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
10. the person who likes turquise is between the person who likes amber and the person who likes grey##2
11. the photographer is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
